        <section>
            <h2>About Michigan</h2>
            <p>Michigan is a state in the Great Lakes and Midwestern regions of the United States. It is known for its beautiful landscapes, freshwater lakes, and vibrant cities.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Fun Facts About Michigan</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Michigan has more than 11,000 inland lakes.</li>
                <li>It is the only state to consist of two peninsulas.</li>
                <li>Detroit, Michigan, is known as the "Motor City" for its role in the automotive industry.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

